works.description: Stern Pinball, the makers of arcade quality pinball machines, has earlier impressed us with their limited edition Avatar Pinball machine. The latest from the house is the “Rolling Stones” pinball machine, which is one of their most impressive and pristine titles to date and pays tribute to the Rock ‘n’ Roll’s greatest band. Designed to appeal to the collectors, casual players and the enthusiasts, the Rolling Stones pinball machine lets players experience the ultimate rock concert under glass.
